(46, 'document', 'text/html', 'Password Protect', 'Password Protect', 'Password Protect', '', 'Password Protect', 1, 0, 0, 3, 0, '', '<h2 class="dec">Password Protection</h2>\r\n<p class="p-bigger">Protecting your privacy is important and so you have the ability to password protect your entire website or individual pages.</p>\r\n<p><img class="justifyright" title="wedding website feature tour" src="assets/templates/wedding/images/img-placeholder-tour.gif" alt="wedding website feature tour" width="453" height="215" />invite text here</p>', 1, 2, 8, 1, 0, 1, 1315518897, 1, 1316685313, 0, 0, 0, 1315518900, 1, 'Password Protect', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'modDocument', 'wedding', 1),
(38, 'document', 'text/html', 'Easy Admin Panel', 'Easy Admin Panel', 'Easy Admin Panel', '', 'Easy Admin Panel', 1, 0, 0, 3, 0, '', '<h2 class="dec">Easy Admin Panel</h2>\r\n<p class="p-bigger">Once you’ve signed up for your wedding website you will be able to log in to your admin panel and start adding content and updating the pre-defined pages.</p>\r\n<p><img class="justifyright" title="wedding website feature tour" src="assets/templates/wedding/images/img-placeholder-tour.gif" alt="wedding website feature tour" width="453" height="215" />The main menu for your website pages is on the left of your admin pages. We have pre selected the 20 most popular titles to get you started. You have a choice to change the titles, turn the pages on or off and password protect individual pages.</p>\r\n<p>You can easily add content whether it be plain text, images or hyperlinks. The editor contains the most popular formatting options such as making text bold, italic or creating headings.</p>', 1, 2, 2, 1, 0, 1, 1315518327, 1, 1315907735, 0, 0, 0, 1315518360, 1, 'Easy Admin Panel', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'modDocument', 'wedding', 1),
