(17, 7, 12, '<p><img title="img" src="images/Blog-images/5.jpg" alt="img" width="500" height="399" />Typography is an essential component of a website’s design. This is for good reason: good typography is not only imperative for aesthetic appeal, but also improves site usability when text legibility and readability concepts are applied. Typography is all about proportions and spacing.</p>'),
